{"tid":912846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「無罪不等於無做」","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T03:40:03.000Z","uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc87cb0c166c756fed1b63a0dc98467b7445ec9c","tid":912846,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=5a6c0909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&h=698b6b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475</a><br />\n<br />\n中央電視台記者孔琳琳，在9月底大鬧英國保守黨在伯明翰舉行的「香港自由、法治、自治受損」座談會，更涉嫌掌摑香港義工。英國警方早前以普通襲擊罪起訴她，但央視證實英國當局已撤銷起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n央視發言人證實，英國檢方昨（20日）午決定對孔琳琳撤訴，孔琳琳的律師已收到檢方通知。律師表示，檢方重新審查孔琳琳被控普通襲擊罪後，認為證據不足，決定撤銷，原定今日舉行的法庭聽證亦取消。<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳是央視歐洲中心站記者，今年9月30日在英國保守黨年會一個有關香港事務的座談會上，大聲叫罵與會者「反華」和「漢奸」，並涉嫌掌摑香港留學生義工被捕。"}]}